WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.920 --> 00:00:04.000
The position of the heir to the Jiang family is really evil.

2
00:00:04.220 --> 00:00:07.490
That’s right. It was necessary to decide the heir twenty years ago.

3
00:00:07.880 --> 00:00:09.000
The eldest son's husband died.

4
00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:10.980
Now I want to appoint my grandson as his heir.

5
00:00:11.410 --> 00:00:13.290
The grandson was poisoned to death by his wife again.

6
00:00:13.620 --> 00:00:16.400
Tell me, will anyone dare to be the heir to the Jiang family from now on?

7
00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:19.160
Of course there is. Who wouldn’t want to inherit the cruelty of a househusband?

8
00:00:19.670 --> 00:00:20.930
Even if you rely on fortune telling, you will go there.

9
00:00:26.420 --> 00:00:29.600
Don't be sad, this kid Jiang Mian has a hard life.

10
00:00:30.140 --> 00:00:31.660
That car accident more than twenty years ago,

11
00:00:32.060 --> 00:00:34.180
If he survives, he has already turned around.

12
00:00:35.370 --> 00:00:38.290
Now it is a kind of relief for him.

13
00:00:38.290 --> 00:00:40.950
What does that mean?

14
00:00:43.180 --> 00:00:44.080
Big brother is gone

15
00:00:44.620 --> 00:00:46.520
You have also been the richest man for more than 20 years.

16
00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:48.480
Jiang Mian is no longer here

17
00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:53.640
The Jiang family will still be the most powerful financial group in Linjiang

18
00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:57.930
With your idiot son

19
00:00:57.930 --> 00:01:01.180
I just pocketed my property.

20
00:01:01.180 --> 00:01:02.260
I can't give it to you either

21
00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:06.340
It's not up to you to say that

22
00:01:06.340 --> 00:01:08.380
It's your turn

23
00:01:10.700 --> 00:01:17.270
Xiaoroufu Butler Feng

24
00:01:17.270 --> 00:01:19.820
Hello, Miss Jiang

25
00:01:19.820 --> 00:01:21.540
this is what you want

26
00:01:23.390 --> 00:01:25.310
Dad, you see clearly

27
00:01:25.590 --> 00:01:27.550
Now I own the Jiang Group

28
00:01:27.550 --> 00:01:29.450
Thirty-one percent of the shares

29
00:01:31.780 --> 00:01:36.010
Everyone, from today onwards, Jiangshi Group is mine!

